msgctxt "84_Gossipy Businessman"
msgid "Did you know there was a murder right near here?"
msgstr "¿Sabías que hubo un asesinato cerca de aquí?"

msgctxt "96_Curious Businesswoman"
msgid "What!? Really!? Did they catch the killer yet?"
msgstr "¿En serio? ¿Atrapan al asesino ya?"

msgctxt "108_Gossipy Businessman"
msgid "I read about it online, but they haven't got the killer yet. Probably already skipped town."
msgstr "Leí sobre esta noticia en línea, pero aún no han atrapado al asesino. Probablemente, ya se haya escapado de Kamurocho."

msgctxt "120_Curious Businesswoman"
msgid "I sure hope so. Still, I think I'll go home early today."
msgstr "Espero que ya no esté en Kamurocho. Aun así, creo que hoy me iré temprano a casa."

